Why This System Exists

Most AI finance tools stop at:
	â€¢	document Q&A
	â€¢	retrieval-augmented chat
	â€¢	static analysis scripts

They fail to address:
	â€¢	institutional memory
	â€¢	multi-agent specialization
	â€¢	cross-company reasoning
	â€¢	capital-level abstraction
	â€¢	verification and auditability
	â€¢	replay and learning over time

NotionWealth Intelligence was designed from the start as a decision platform, not a document tool.

