Running the System

1. Install dependencies

pip install -r requirements.txt

2. Add API key

Create .env:

GOOGLE_API_KEY=your_key_here

3. Ingest documents

Place PDFs into:

data/raw/

Run ingestion or use UI.

â¸»

4. Start MCP server

python mcp_server.py


â¸»

5. Launch UI

streamlit run finance-agent/ui/app.py


â¸»

Research Artifacts

Every research run generates:
	â€¢	a structured research session
	â€¢	evidence links
	â€¢	agent execution traces
	â€¢	optional replay capability

This enables:
	â€¢	auditability
	â€¢	verification
	â€¢	institutional learning
	â€¢	decision history

â¸»

Design Philosophy
	â€¢	Agents are specialists, not prompts
	â€¢	Memory is stratified, not flat
	â€¢	Verification is mandatory
	â€¢	Traces are first-class artifacts
	â€¢	Replay is a core system primitive
	â€¢	Outputs are decision surfaces, not answers

